        <item>
            <title>1.12.0</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h3>Fixes across Focus, capture, Week view, and Media.</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><b>Focus is today-only</b> — future-dated tasks no longer clutter your Focus board</li>
                    <li><b>Cleaner capture</b> — a <b>#project</b> tag is stripped from the title (it stays a chip, not literal text)</li>
                    <li><b>Week-view events are clickable again</b> on Mac — tap to edit</li>
                    <li><b>Steadier Media covers</b> on Mac — no more flashing/reloading posters</li>
                    <li><b>Ongoing projects</b> can now choose whether new tasks start active or on hold</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
